@startuml Recruiter_Company

title Recruiter - Company Management (Module B)

actor Recruiter as "👔 Nhà Tuyển Dụng"

rectangle "COMPANY" {
    usecase "Create New\nCompany" as B1
    usecase "List My\nCompanies" as B2
    usecase "View Company\nDetails" as B3
    usecase "Update Company\nInfo" as B4
    usecase "Delete Company" as B5
    usecase "Verify Tax ID" as B6
    usecase "Add Industry\nCategory" as B7
    usecase "View Company\nIndustries" as B8
    usecase "View System\nIndustries" as B9
}

Recruiter --> B1: 1. Create company
Recruiter --> B2: 2. List companies
B2 --> B3: View details
B3 --> B4: 3. Update info
B3 --> B5: 4. Delete company
B3 --> B6: 5. Verify tax ID
B3 --> B7: 6. Add industry
B3 --> B8: View industries
Recruiter --> B9: View system industries

note right of B1
  **Priority:** P0 (Critical)
  **Status:** Need Validation
end note

@enduml
